name: Supporting Zuzalu Projects Dinner
description:
Many projects are being launched at Zuzalu! 

For anyone who wants to support these projects, we will discuss how to collaborate, help people set up their Gitcoin passports (takes five minutes), and then donations to these projects will be matched by Gitcoin quadratically. 

If a group of 10 people each donates 10 dollars to a project that can raise thousands of dollars of matched funds for that project.
